
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Voodoo Players Club — Join the League</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@400;700;900&family=Crimson+Text:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&family=Oswald:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap');

  :root {
    --black: #0a0a0a;
    --dark: #111111;
    --card: #161616;
    --card2: #1c1a1e;
    --purple: #7B4FBF;
    --purple-light: #9B6FDF;
    --purple-dark: #4a2d80;
    --cream: #F0EAD6;
    --cream-muted: #c8bfa8;
    --gold: #D4A843;
    --border: rgba(123,79,191,0.3);
    --border-light: rgba(240,234,214,0.12);
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    background: var(--black);
    color: var(--cream);
    font-family: 'Crimson Text', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .page {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: var(--dark);
    border-left: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .hero {
    background: var(--black);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 60px 60px 52px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--purple);
  }

  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, rgba(123,79,191,0.2) 0%, transparent 65%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .logo-wrap {
    margin: 0 auto 28px;
    width: 160px; height: 160px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px solid var(--purple);
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    background: #000;
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
    box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(123,79,191,0.3);
  }
  .logo-wrap img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 5px; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--purple-light); margin-bottom: 10px;
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 52px; font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--cream); line-height: 1.05;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    text-shadow: 0 0 60px rgba(123,79,191,0.5);
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 20px; font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--purple-light); letter-spacing: 3px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-tagline {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 4px; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--cream-muted);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 12px 0; display: inline-block; width: 100%;
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }
  .hero-tagline span { color: var(--purple-light); margin: 0 12px; }

  /* ── HOOK ── */
  .hook {
    background: var(--purple-dark);
    padding: 24px 60px;
    text-align: center;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .hook p {
    font-family: 'Crimson Text', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 20px; font-style: italic;
    color: var(--cream); line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .hook strong { font-style: normal; color: var(--gold); }

  /* ── SECTION ── */
  .section { padding: 50px 60px 0; }

  .section-label {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 5px; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--purple-light); margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--cream);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--purple-dark);
    padding-bottom: 12px; margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .section-title .accent { color: var(--purple-light); }

  .body-text {
    font-family: 'Crimson Text', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--cream-muted);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .body-text strong { color: var(--cream); font-weight: 600; }

  /* ── DIVIDER ── */
  .divider {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
    margin: 48px 60px 0; opacity: 0.4;
  }
  .divider-line { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--border-light); }
  .divider-diamond { color: var(--purple); font-size: 14px; }

  /* ── SHOW UP STEPS ── */
  .steps {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 16px; margin-top: 24px;
  }

  .step {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-top: 3px solid var(--purple);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 24px 20px; text-align: center;
  }

  .step-num {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 28px; font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--purple-light); line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .step h4 {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--cream); margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .step p {
    font-family: 'Crimson Text', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 15px; color: var(--cream-muted); line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* ── NIGHT SCHEDULE ── */
  .schedule-card {
    background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; margin-top: 24px;
  }

  .schedule-header {
    background: var(--purple-dark); padding: 12px 24px;
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 4px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--cream);
  }

  .schedule-row {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 24px;
    padding: 16px 24px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  }
  .schedule-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .sched-time {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--purple-light); min-width: 60px;
  }

  .sched-dot {
    width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--purple); flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .sched-text h5 {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--cream); margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .sched-text p {
    font-family: 'Crimson Text', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 15px; color: var(--cream-muted);
  }

  /* ── SEASON SECTION ── */
  .season-split {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 20px; margin-top: 24px;
  }

  .season-card {
    background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px; padding: 24px 22px;
  }

  .season-card .card-icon { font-size: 26px; margin-bottom: 12px; display: block; }

  .season-card h4 {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--cream); margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .season-card p {
    font-family: 'Crimson Text', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 16px; color: var(--cream-muted); line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .season-card p strong { color: var(--cream); }

  /* ── POINTS ── */
  .points-row {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 12px; margin-top: 24px;
  }

  .pt-card {
    background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px 14px; text-align: center;
  }

  .pt-card .pts {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 32px; font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--purple-light); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .pt-card .pts.gold { color: var(--gold); }

  .pt-card .label {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--cream-muted);
  }

  .callout {
    background: var(--card); border-left: 3px solid var(--purple);
    border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0; padding: 20px 24px; margin: 24px 0;
  }
  .callout p {
    font-family: 'Crimson Text', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.75; color: var(--cream-muted); font-style: italic;
  }
  .callout p strong { color: var(--cream); font-style: normal; }

  /* ── CTA ── */
  .cta {
    background: var(--black); border-top: 2px solid var(--purple-dark);
    margin-top: 60px; padding: 56px 60px; text-align: center;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .cta::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 100%, rgba(123,79,191,0.15) 0%, transparent 65%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .cta-eyebrow {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 5px; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--purple-light); margin-bottom: 14px;
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }

  .cta h2 {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 34px; font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--cream); margin-bottom: 16px;
    text-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(123,79,191,0.4);
    line-height: 1.2; position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }

  .cta p {
    font-family: 'Crimson Text', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 18px; color: var(--cream-muted); font-style: italic;
    max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto 32px; line-height: 1.8;
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }

  .cta-details {
    display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 36px; flex-wrap: wrap;
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }

  .cta-detail .d-label {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 4px; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--cream-muted); margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .cta-detail .d-val {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gold);
  }

  .cta-btn {
    display: inline-block; background: var(--purple); color: var(--cream);
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase; padding: 16px 44px; border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none; border: 1px solid var(--purple-light); cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
    box-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(123,79,191,0.3);
  }
  .cta-btn:hover { background: var(--purple-light); box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(123,79,191,0.5); }

  .cta-note {
    font-family: 'Crimson Text', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 15px; color: rgba(200,191,168,0.6); font-style: italic;
    margin-top: 14px; position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }

  .footer-badge {
    display: inline-block; background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 100px; padding: 10px 28px;
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--purple-light);
    margin-top: 32px; position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }

  .page-foot {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 3px;
    color: rgba(240,234,214,0.15); text-align: center;
    padding: 16px 0 4px; position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="logo-wrap">
      <img src="https://i.imgur.com/xIHZB7o.png" alt="Voodoo Players Club" id="logo-img">
    </div>
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">Thursday Nights · The Voodoo Cellar</div>
    <div class="hero-title">Voodoo Players<br>Club</div>
    <div class="hero-sub">Beer Pong League</div>
    <div class="hero-tagline">
      Team Play <span>✦</span> Good People <span>✦</span> No Drama
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- HOOK -->
  <div class="hook">
    <p>Show up Thursday, grab a partner, and play. <strong>No experience needed — just bring a good time.</strong></p>
  </div>

  <!-- SHOW UP -->
  <div class="section">

    <p class="body-text">
      There's a spot for everyone on Thursday nights. Whether you want a casual game or you're chasing a championship, just walk through the door and we'll get you sorted.
    </p>
    <div class="steps" style="grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;">
      <div class="step">
        <div style="font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 12px;">🍺</div>
        <h4>Free Play</h4>
        <p>Just here for a good time? Jump in for casual games, no strings attached. Grab a drink, find a table, and play at your own pace all night long.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step" style="border-top-color: var(--gold);">
        <div style="font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 12px;">🏆</div>
        <h4>League Play</h4>
        <p>Register your team and compete in a <strong style="color: var(--cream);">double elimination tournament</strong> 🎯 — earn points win or lose, track your standing all month, and chase the Monthly Championship. 🥇</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="callout" style="margin-top: 28px;">
      <p>No partner? <strong>No problem.</strong> Come solo and we'll pair you up. The only thing you need to bring is yourself.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="divider"><div class="divider-line"></div><div class="divider-diamond">◆</div><div class="divider-line"></div></div>

  <!-- NIGHT SCHEDULE -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-label">Every Thursday</div>
    <div class="section-title">How the <span class="accent">Night Runs</span></div>
    <div class="schedule-card">
      <div class="schedule-header">📅 &nbsp;League Night · 8 PM Until a Champion is Crowned 👑</div>
      <div class="schedule-row">
        <div class="sched-time">8:00</div>
        <div class="sched-dot"></div>
        <div class="sched-text">
          <h5>Doors & Check-In</h5>
          <p>Walk in, check in, grab a drink. Meet your opponents for the night.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="schedule-row">
        <div class="sched-time">8:30</div>
        <div class="sched-dot"></div>
        <div class="sched-text">
          <h5>Matches Begin</h5>
          <p>The double elimination tournament kicks off — earn points win or lose, and you've always got a second chance.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="schedule-row">
        <div class="sched-time">10:15</div>
        <div class="sched-dot" style="background: var(--gold);"></div>
        <div class="sched-text">
          <h5 style="color: var(--gold);">Night Final</h5>
          <p>The top teams from the evening face off for the Night Winner title and bonus points.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="divider"><div class="divider-line"></div><div class="divider-diamond">◆</div><div class="divider-line"></div></div>

  <!-- SEASON SYSTEM -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-label">Keep Coming Back</div>
    <div class="section-title">One Night Is Fun. <span class="accent">A Season Is a Story.</span></div>
    <p class="body-text">
      Every Thursday night counts toward the monthly standings. The more you show up, the more you earn — and at the end of each month, the league crowns its champions.
    </p>

    <div class="season-split">
      <div class="season-card">
        <span class="card-icon">📅</span>
        <h4>Monthly Seasons</h4>
        <p>Each month is its own season — four Thursday nights building toward a <strong>Monthly Championship on Week 4.</strong> Fresh start every month means anyone can rise.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="season-card">
        <span class="card-icon">🏆</span>
        <h4>Something to Play For</h4>
        <p>Monthly titles for Top Team, Top Player, Most Consistent, and community-voted <strong>Best Vibes.</strong> Recognition that goes beyond the win/loss record.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="points-row">
      <div class="pt-card">
        <div class="pts">+1</div>
        <div class="label">Just Show Up</div>
      </div>
      <div class="pt-card">
        <div class="pts">+2</div>
        <div class="label">Win a Match</div>
      </div>
      <div class="pt-card">
        <div class="pts">+1</div>
        <div class="label">Lose a Match</div>
      </div>
      <div class="pt-card">
        <div class="pts gold">+3</div>
        <div class="label">Night Winner</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="callout">
      <p>Points are tracked per player, not just per team — so even if your usual partner can't make it, <strong>your season keeps rolling.</strong> No wasted Thursdays.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <div class="cta">
    <div class="cta-eyebrow">Thursday Nights · The Voodoo Cellar</div>
    <h2>Boise's Best Night<br>of Beer Pong.</h2>
    <p>Unique drinks, good people, and the best beer pong in Boise. Don't be spooked — come see what we're about.</p>

    <div class="cta-details">
      <div class="cta-detail">
        <div class="d-label">When</div>
        <div class="d-val">Thursdays</div>
      </div>
      <div class="cta-detail">
        <div class="d-label">Check-In</div>
        <div class="d-val">8:00 PM</div>
      </div>
      <div class="cta-detail">
        <div class="d-label">Where</div>
        <div class="d-val">The Voodoo Cellar</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-badge">Team Play · Good People · No Drama</div>
    <div class="page-foot">The Voodoo Players Club — Beer Pong League at The Voodoo Cellar</div>
  </div>

</div>

<script>
  const img = document.getElementById('logo-img');
  img.onerror = function() {
    this.style.display = 'none';
    this.parentElement.innerHTML = '<div style="font-family:serif;font-size:48px;color:#7B4FBF;text-align:center;line-height:160px;">☠</div>';
  };
</script>
</body>
</html>
